Detailed Description

template<class T, class U, MODULE ID, PARAM_TYPE PT>
class ePhotosynthesis::ValueSetStatic< T, U, ID, PT >

Template class to provide methods for manipulating a set of static class values used by a model run that can be set via input files.

Template Parameters
TChild class with virtual & static methods.
UParent class with virtual & static methods.
IDEnum corresponding to the module that the values will be used by.
PTEnum corresponding to the module component that the values will be used by.
